&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-42"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;    """&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-43"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="n"&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-44"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;colnumgenerator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-45"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;        &lt;span class="n"&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-46"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;        &lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;colnum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_02a0523dad0b4640a46e2f98619df3c9-47"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;            &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;</description><category>Excel</category><category>Python</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythonshi-xian-excellie-ming-he-xia-biao-de-xiang-hu-zhuan-huan/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2017 16:17:58 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>夜饮微醺</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-yin-wei-xun/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;此心憔悴不思量，望家长盼浣纱娘。&lt;/p&gt;
